reviewText: Although the video played on my computer, it did not play in my DVD player ... other DVDs play fine in my DVD player, but this one does not.

studying for my 3rd kyu in aikido along with my son we are always told if you don't know the basics you will not be able to do the advanced techniques. in this 3rd dvd in his series he goes over ikkyo nikkyo sankyo yonkyo and gokyo I would recommend this to anyone interested in aikido.
